                                <div id="printAreaContent" class="printAreaContent" tabindex="-1">
                                    
    
        <div class="fbg-row lmRow ui-sortable" data-lm-customclass=""><div data-lm-columnwidth="3" class="lmColumn ui-sortable fbg-col-xs-12 fbg-col-sm-12 fbg-col-md-6 fbg-col-lg-3 column" data-lm-customclass=""><div class="ge-content ge-content-type-gridHTML ui-droppable" data-ge-content-type="gridHTML"><div class="fbg-container-fluid ImageboxOneColumn lmLayoutComponent" data-lm-id="lm1617915587606" data-lm-componenttype="ImageboxOneColumn" data-lm-componenttitle=""><div class="iCreateNoneditableToken" data-lm-tokenid="ImageboxOneColumnTK1" data-icrt-tk-cfg="PlainContent" id="ImageboxOneColumnTK1_lm1617915587606"><div class="fbg-row lb-imageBox cm-datacontainer" data-cm-itemdata="{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;featuredImage&quot;:&quot;/en/government/resources/Documents/council-town-administration/Headshot-Photos/CaledonMayor-AnnetteGroves_OfficialPortrait-96dpi.jpg&quot;,&quot;featuredImageAlt&quot;:&quot;Mayor&quot;,&quot;boxHeading&quot;:&quot;Mayor Annette Groves&quot;,&quot;linkUrl&quot;:&quot;/en/government/mayor.aspx&quot;,&quot;boxContent&quot;:&quot;<p><a class=\&quot;defaultButton-Secondary\&quot; title=\&quot;View Mayoral Decisions\&quot; href=\&quot;https://www.caledon.ca/en/government/mayoral-decisions.aspx\&quot;>Mayoral Decisions</a></p>&quot;}]}"><div class="fbg-col-xs-12"><a href="/en/government/mayor.aspx" target="{linkTarget}" title="Mayor Annette Groves"><img src="/en/government/resources/Documents/council-town-administration/Headshot-Photos/CaledonMayor-AnnetteGroves_OfficialPortrait-96dpi.jpg" alt="Mayor"><div class="lb-imageBox_header {headColor}">Mayor Annette Groves</div></a><div class="lb-imageBox_content"><p><a class="defaultButton-Secondary" title="View Mayoral Decisions" href="/en/government/mayoral-decisions.aspx">Mayoral Decisions</a></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-lm-columnwidth="9" class="lmColumn ui-sortable fbg-col-xs-12 fbg-col-sm-9 column" data-lm-customclass=""><div class="ge-content ge-content-type-gridHTML ui-droppable" data-ge-content-type="gridHTML"><div class="fbg-container-fluid lmLayoutComponent" data-lm-id="lm1617915590429" data-lm-componenttype="StandardOneColumn" data-lm-componenttitle=""><div class="fbg-row"><div class="fbg-col-xs-12"><div class="iCreateDynaToken" data-lm-tokenid="StandardOneColumnTK1" data-icrt-tk-cfg="StandardColumnContent" id="StandardOneColumnTK1_lm1617915590429"><h2>Welcome</h2>
<div>
<p>On behalf of the Members of Council, thank you for your interest in YOUR government. On this page you can learn more about how Caledon Council works, our work plan, and a little bit about who we are.</p>
<p>Our vision is to continue to celebrate Caledons rich history while also preserving the unique communities within our villages.&nbsp; We are committed to protecting our valuable landscapes and growing the Town of Caledon into a place that unites our communities.&nbsp; But, we need your help and support on this journey!</p>
<p>&nbsp;<em>Annette</em></p>
</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="fbg-row lmRow ui-sortable" data-lm-customclass=""><div data-lm-columnwidth="4" class="lmColumn ui-sortable fbg-col-xs-12 fbg-col-sm-4 column" data-lm-customclass=""><div class="ge-content ge-content-type-gridHTML ui-droppable" data-ge-content-type="gridHTML"><div class="fbg-container-fluid lmLayoutComponent" data-lm-id="lm1624977690945" data-lm-componenttype="StandardOneColumn" data-lm-componenttitle=""><div class="fbg-row"><div class="fbg-col-xs-12"><div class="iCreateDynaToken" data-lm-tokenid="StandardOneColumnTK1" data-icrt-tk-cfg="StandardColumnContent" id="StandardOneColumnTK1_lm1624977690945"><h2>Watch Council</h2>
<p>Council meetings are streamed live. View agendas, minutes and the live stream at&nbsp;<a title="View our Agendas and Minutes page" href="/en/government/agendas-and-minutes.aspx">caledon.ca/agenda</a>.</p>
<p><a class="defaultButton-Secondary" title="View our Agendas and Minutes page" href="/en/government/agendas-and-minutes.aspx">Council schedule</a></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-lm-columnwidth="4" class="lmColumn ui-sortable fbg-col-xs-12 fbg-col-sm-4 column" data-lm-customclass=""><div class="ge-content ge-content-type-gridHTML ui-droppable" data-ge-content-type="gridHTML"><div class="fbg-container-fluid lmLayoutComponent" data-lm-id="lm1617051430459" data-lm-componenttype="StandardOneColumn" data-lm-componenttitle=""><div class="fbg-row"><div class="fbg-col-xs-12"><div class="iCreateDynaToken" data-lm-tokenid="StandardOneColumnTK1" data-icrt-tk-cfg="StandardColumnContent" id="StandardOneColumnTK1_lm1617051430459"><h2>Get involved</h2>
<p>If you wish to make your voice heard, you can participate in Council proceedings in several ways, both in person and in writing.</p>
<p><a class="defaultButton-Secondary" title="Delegate or present to Council" href="/en/government/get-involved.aspx">Get involved</a></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-lm-columnwidth="4" class="lmColumn ui-sortable fbg-col-xs-12 fbg-col-sm-4 column" data-lm-customclass=""><div class="ge-content ge-content-type-gridHTML ui-droppable" data-ge-content-type="gridHTML"><div class="fbg-container-fluid lmLayoutComponent" data-lm-id="lm1618932352282" data-lm-componenttype="StandardOneColumn" data-lm-componenttitle=""><div class="fbg-row"><div class="fbg-col-xs-12"><div class="iCreateDynaToken" data-lm-tokenid="StandardOneColumnTK1" data-icrt-tk-cfg="StandardColumnContent" id="StandardOneColumnTK1_lm1618932352282"><h2>Meet your Council</h2>
<p>The Town is divided into six wards with one local&nbsp;Councillor each and two Regional Councillors (wards 1,2,3 and 4,5,6.)</p>
<p><a class="defaultButton-Primary" title="Open new window to view Find your ward" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://caledon.maps.arcgis.com/apps/View/index.html?appid=054d27d1d8d7434c96477399549d3c7f" target="_blank" aria-label="Find your ward opens in new window">Find your ward</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="fbg-row lmRow ui-sortable" data-lm-customclass=""><div data-lm-columnwidth="3" class="lmColumn ui-sortable fbg-col-xs-12 fbg-col-sm-12 fbg-col-md-6 fbg-col-lg-3 column" data-lm-customclass=""><div class="ge-content ge-content-type-gridHTML ui-droppable" data-ge-content-type="gridHTML"><div class="fbg-container-fluid ImageboxOneColumn lmLayoutComponent" data-lm-id="lm1618930145376" data-lm-componenttype="ImageboxOneColumn" data-lm-componenttitle=""><div class="iCreateNoneditableToken" data-lm-tokenid="ImageboxOneColumnTK1" data-icrt-tk-cfg="PlainContent" id="ImageboxOneColumnTK1_lm1618930145376"><div class="fbg-row lb-imageBox cm-datacontainer" data-cm-itemdata="{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;featuredImage&quot;:&quot;/en/government/resources/Documents/council-town-administration/Headshot-Photos/EAL_5544.jpg&quot;,&quot;featuredImageAlt&quot;:&quot;Ward 1, 2 &amp; 3 Regional Councillor Christina Early&quot;,&quot;boxHeading&quot;:&quot;Wards 1, 2 &amp; 3 Regional Councillor Christina Early&quot;,&quot;linkUrl&quot;:&quot;https://www.caledon.ca/en/government/ward-1-regional-councillor.aspx&quot;,&quot;linkTarget&quot;:&quot;_blank&quot;,&quot;boxContent&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]}"><div class="fbg-col-xs-12"><a href="/en/government/ward-1-regional-councillor.aspx" target="_blank" title="Wards 1, 2 &amp; 3 Regional Councillor Christina Early" aria-label="Wards 1, 2 &amp; 3 Regional Councillor Christina Early opens in new window"><img src="/en/government/resources/Documents/council-town-administration/Headshot-Photos/EAL_5544.jpg" alt="Ward 1, 2 &amp; 3 Regional Councillor Christina Early"><div class="lb-imageBox_header {headColor}">Wards 1, 2 &amp; 3 Regional Councillor Christina Early</div></a><div class="lb-imageBox_content"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-lm-columnwidth="3" class="lmColumn ui-sortable fbg-col-xs-12 fbg-col-sm-12 fbg-col-md-6 fbg-col-lg-3 column" data-lm-customclass=""><div 